Patch-mainline: v6.6-rc1
References: perf-v6.7 (jsc#PED-6012 jsc#PED-6121)

loc is passed as NULL in tools/perf/tests/bpf.c do_test, meaning
errors trigger a SEGV when trying to access. Add the missing NULL
check.

